filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class="reviewer">\n				By <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/camerah"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/6f896b9d48c8d6ce68706df0dd6c0622?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/6f896b9d48c8d6ce68706df0dd6c0622?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/camerah" class="reviewer-name">Camerah</a> on <span class="review-date">June 4, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class="review-body">We often are not keeping track of resizing our images before uploading and this plugin was recommended to us through many review articles online. We tried it out and love how much space it has saved us and the majority of the images look great in their compressed state.</div>\n</div>\n";}s:17:"short_description";s:129:"Automatically compress, optimize and serve scaled images along with next-gen WebP all from CloudFront CDN. Lazy load included ⚡";s:13:"download_link";s:54:"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/optimole-wp.zip";s:11:"screenshots";a:4:{i:1;a:2:{s:3:"src";s:65:"https://ps.w.org/optimole-wp/assets/screenshot-1.jpeg?rev=2177067";s:7:"caption";s:14:"Welcome screen";}i:2;a:2:{s:3:"src";s:65:"https://ps.w.org/optimole-wp/assets/screenshot-2.jpeg?rev=1991521";s:7:"caption";s:14:"Connect screen";}i:3;a:2:{s:3:"src";s:65:"https://ps.w.org/optimole-wp/assets/screenshot-3.jpeg?rev=2177067";s:7:"caption";s:16:"Plugin dashboard";}i:4;a:2:{s:3:"src";s:65:"https://ps.w.org/optimole-wp/assets/screenshot-4.jpeg?rev=2177067";s:7:"caption";s:15:"Plugin settings";}}s:8:"versions";a:33:{s:5:"1.0.1";s:60:"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/optimole-wp.1.0.1.zip";s:5:"1.0.2";s:60:"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/optimole-wp.1.0.2.zip";